# ============================================================================
# WarungTech AI Assistant - Environment Variables
# ============================================================================

# REQUIRED: OpenRouter API Key for LLM access
# Get your key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Sign up at: https://openrouter.ai/
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-openrouter-api-key-here

# OPTIONAL: Infura Project ID for Ethereum/Web3 features
# Get your project ID from: https://infura.io/
# Sign up at: https://infura.io/register
# This enables blockchain coupon features
INFURA_PROJECT_ID=your-infura-project-id-here

# ============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================================================

# 1. OPENROUTER API KEY (REQUIRED)
#    - Go to https://openrouter.ai/keys
#    - Create account if needed
#    - Generate new API key
#    - Copy and paste above (starts with sk-or-v1-)
#    - This enables AI chat functionality

# 2. INFURA PROJECT ID (OPTIONAL - for blockchain features)
#    - Go to https://infura.io/register
#    - Create free account
#    - Create new project (Ethereum)
#    - Copy Project ID from dashboard
#    - This enables smart contract coupon features

# 3. RENAME THIS FILE
#    - Rename .env.example to .env
#    - Add your actual keys above
#    - Never commit .env to git (already in .gitignore)

# ============================================================================
# FEATURE AVAILABILITY
# ============================================================================

# With OPENROUTER_API_KEY only:
# ✅ Business analysis from WarungTech API
# ✅ Financial summary and recommendations  
# ✅ Investment portfolio analysis
# ✅ Real-time crypto market data
# ✅ AI-powered business insights
# ❌ Blockchain coupon features (disabled)

# With BOTH keys:
# ✅ All above features
# ✅ Smart contract coupon statistics
# ✅ Blockchain promo management
# ✅ Web3 wallet integration

# ============================================================================
# COST INFORMATION
# ============================================================================

# OpenRouter API:
# - Pay-per-use model
# - ~$0.001-0.01 per request depending on model
# - Free tier available for testing
# - Supports multiple AI models

# Infura:
# - Free tier: 100,000 requests/day
# - More than enough for typical usage
# - No cost for read-only operations

# ============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ============================================================================

# - Keep your API keys secure
# - Never share or commit to version control
# - Rotate keys periodically
# - Monitor usage on provider dashboards
# - Use environment variables in production